        public Class<? extends org.apache.wicket.Page> getPageIdentity()
        Description copied from interface: IPageLink
        Gets the class of the destination page, which serves as a form of identity that can be used to determine if a link is on the same Page that it links to.

        A page's identity is used if the user is allowed to visit the target page.
